# TypeScript incremental build cache — regenerates on every build.
*.tsbuildinfo

# Agent-generated artifacts at the repo root. The dev-server starts
# in this directory, so any agent that writes to its cwd (CRM
# enrichment agents typically write dossiers, summaries, quick refs)
# drops files here. They're test/run outputs, not source.
/*_dossier.md
/*_dossier.json
/*_SUMMARY.md
/*_REFERENCE.md
/*_INDEX.md
/dossier_*.md
/dossier_*.json
